ential issue where `Build.VERSION` lacks `SDK_INT`, causing a `NoSuchFieldException`.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented a dedicated test for `org.springframework.objenesis.strategy.PlatformDescription`.\n\nChanged:\n- Added `tests/src/org.springframework/spring-core/5.3.15/src/test/java/android/os/PlatformDescriptionTest.java`\n\nWhat it covers:\n- Simulates legacy Android/Dalvik by setting `java.vm.name` to `Dalvik`.\n- Provides an `android.os.Build.VERSION` test fixture with only the legacy `SDK` field and no `SDK_INT`.\n- Loads `PlatformDescription` through an isolated child-first class loader so static initialization reaches the old Android fallback path.\n- Exercises:\n  - `Class#getField(\"SDK\")`\n  - `Field#get(null)`\n- Handles unsupported Native Image dynamic class loading via `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError`.\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per your instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0bf3cca24f07cf870169f5a6d122c4819d8c674ff57ac44bed\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1568, "output": 793, "cacheRead": 28160, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30521, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777706695375, "responseId": "resp_0bf3cca24f07cf870169f5a6c7d45c819d8ab35311d38b1968"}, "toolResults": []}
